snippet.title: Arcade Game: Jungler (1981 Konami)
snippet.description:
A maze shooting game you control a snake-like ship moving around a number of mazes chasing 3 similar computer controlled ships. Being hit by bullets reduces the length of the ships. Ships are destroyed either when their length is reduced to zero or when they collide with a longer ship.

The game is endless.
